content:
dheaton-arm opened PR #4943 from isle-branch to main:

Ported the existing implementations of the following opcodes for AArch64 to ISLE:

  • Brz
  • Brnz
  • Brif
  • Brff
  • BrIcmp
  • Jump
  • BrTable
